  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "Slice the crispy bread into 1-inch (2.5 cm) thick slices.",
    "Toast the bread slices in the oven for 5-7 minutes, or until crispy.",
    "Meanwhile, mash the avocado in a bowl with a fork until smooth.",
    "Add the vegan mayonnaise, salt, and a sprinkle of fresh dill to the bowl with the mashed avocado.",
    "Mix well to combine.",
    "Once the bread is toasted, spread a layer of the avocado mixture onto each slice.",
    "Top each slice with a slice of tomato and a sprinkle of red onion.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
